---
title: Korean-Style Chicken Patties with Sesame-Green Onion Rice, Carrots and Edamame
description: Gochujang is the star ingredient that takes this dish over the top. Succulent chicken patties are tossed in a sauce consisting of gochujang, soy sauce and honey, then paired with a dynamic veggie duo of carrots and edamame.
